
                              OCR S3 Project
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

                                Description

This project is crossword solver based on a photo. The image is cleaned and,
using AI, it will recognized words and letters. At the end your crossword
get solved;

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

                                HOW TO USE

- Ecexute the binary file "Afflelou" -> $ ./Afflelou
- Click on the "Load image" button
- Load your crossword image format png or jpg

!! Your images will be put in Grid/Modified !!

- Click "preprocess" so your image get clean
- Click "detect line" to detect your lines on the grid
- Click "rotate" and rotate your image for your grid to be in the correct way
- Your done !

!! OCR is comming soon !!

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
